item.title: Cookie Policy
item.description: Cookie Policy for Bunnie ABC Introduction This Cookie Policy explains what cookies are and how Bunnie ABC uses them on our website, located at blog.bunnieabc.com. What Are Cookies? Cookies are small data files that are placed on your device by a website when you visit it. They are widely used to make websites work more efficiently and to provide website owners with information about how their sites are used. How We Use Cookies We use cookies for a number of different purposes.
